                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="143r" to="149r" facs="143"/>
                    <title>I Bow Down</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      እሰግድ፡ ለኪ፡ እግዝእትየ፡ ማርያም፡ ሰርከ፡ ወነግሃ፡ ወእዌድስ፡ ማኅፀንኪ፡
                    </incipit>
                    <note>copied in a different hand of the 19th century, arranged for the days of the week</note>

                    <colophon xml:id="coloph1">
                      <locus target="149r" facs="149">f. 149r, column 2, middle</locus>
                      Including note of ownership,
                      <foreign xml:lang="gez">
                        ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘአካለ፡ ቃል፡ ወአቡሁ፡ ምዕመነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወለእሙ፡ ማርያም፡ ዘመዳ።
                        ወልዱ፡ ዘዜና፡ ማርቆስ። ።
                        ኢትርሥአኒ፡ አቡየ።</foreign>
                        <q>“The book of Akala Qal and his father, Zazyna Krestos and to his mother Mary Zamada and his son Zazena Marqos</q>

                    </colophon>

                  </msItem>
